text: Josianne Fleming-Artsen (born 1949) is an educator and politician, who served as Minister Plenipotentiary of Sint Maarten from 2014 to 2015 and Deputy Minister Plenipotentiary of Sint Maarten from 2013 to 2014. She served as president of the University of St. Martin from 1999 to 2010. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Sint Maarten women in politics Category:Ministers plenipotentiary (Sint Maarten) Category:United People's Party (Sint Maarten) politicians Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:1949 births
